title: Golfer hits fantastic bunker shot between legs
text:
Golfer hits fantastic bunker shot between legs PGA 9 hrs ago T.J. Auclair Â© Provided by PGA As if a shot out of a pot bunker wasn't difficult enough, how about executing a gorgeous shot... from between your legs?
RELATED: Alvaro Quiros gets rejected by cup on tap-in putt
AdChoices That's what Jonathan Day of Essex was able to pull off in this Instagram video: Trick shot Wednesday #trickshot #golftrickshot
Impressive.
